<note id="fs-idm351284160" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm443667088"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 6.3 Westward Expansion: Cultural and Cultural Development</para>
<para id="fs-idm476595216"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: MIG Migration and Settlement</para>
<para id="fs-idm442266320"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 6B Explain the causes and effects of the settlement of the West from 1877 to 1898</para>
<para id="fs-idm466351824"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Developments</emphasis>: 6.2.II.D, 6.2.II.E</para>
<para id="fs-idm499558816"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
